{
  "stem": "18575.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 370.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the kiosks, were all confiscated when it came out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was not a public, except the last weeks was the propaganda that the war is imminent, nothing to be afraid of.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We will stop them, you know, things of that sort.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are ersatz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just before the war started, 1939, I remember the conversation in the family, in large, my father, in fact, wanted to get out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He felt that there's a danger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was an international exhibit, an international fair, in the United States in 1939 in September in that year in that month.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you could obtain American visas for the-- for the fair, the international fair, without any problem, as long as you had the money to travel there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he wanted to go on the visa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if any war breaks out, then, of course, you're stuck in United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As I recall it, and I was later told when we were in Soviet Union by my brother and my father, that supposedly my mother didn't wanted to leave her sister.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She didn't wanted to break the family up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was-- she was not saying outright no but was not ready then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She wanted to think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then, of course, the war broke out, and the whole thing fell apart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that on the September 1-- prior to September 1, of course, there was a call for a week, two weeks before for anybody that could help to dig anti-tank ditches around Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, we young kids, being very patriotic, we all volunteered and dug ditches and-- outside Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought us by trolleys there and told us how to make gas mask out of gauze.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
